            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Hd1e108">Rubrica 27</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De penitentia et congtritione peccatorum</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e114">
              De peccatorum contritione 
              <lb ed="#C"/><!--text shares a line with the next paragraph-->et penitentia capitulum
            </p>
            <p>
              Psalmista psalmo V
              <lb ed="#C"/>Dominus saluos nos fecit rec<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tos 
              corde
            </p>
            <p>
              ¶ Idem IX patientia pauperum
              <lb ed="#C"/>non probit in finem
            </p>
            <p>
              ¶ Idem XIII Domine
              <lb ed="#C"/>quis habitabit in tabernaculo
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e121">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Rd1e118">34</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e125">Ius<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tus 
              est dominus hys qui sunt tribulato
              <lb ed="#C"/>corde et humiles spiritu saluabit multe tri<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>bulationes 
              instorum et de his omnibus
              <lb ed="#C"/>liberabit eos</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e139">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Rd1e141">Idem CXLVII</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e141">qui seminant
              <lb ed="#C"/>in lachrymis in exultatione metent</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e148">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Rd1e154">Eze<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>chiel
              capitulo 18</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e152">Si impius egerit penitentiam de omnibus
              <lb ed="#C"/>peccatis suis que operatus est et custodierit
              <lb ed="#C"/>omnia precepta mea et fecerit iudicium et iusti<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tiam 
              uita uiuet et non morietur et omnium
              <lb ed="#C"/>iniquitatum eius quas operatus est non re<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>cordabor
              ¶ Ait dominus Ibidem Conuer<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>timini 
              et agite penitentiam ab omnibus iniquitati<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>bus 
              uestris et non est uobis in ruinam iniqui<pb ed="#C" n="11-v"/><cb ed="#C" n="a"/><lb ed="#C"/>tas </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e173">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Rd1e181">Yesus filius sydrach in ecclesiastico capitulo</ref> 
              <lb ed="#C"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e177">Altissimus odio habet peccatores et
              <lb ed="#C"/>misertus est penitentibus</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e185">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Rd1e195">Mattheus in
              <lb ed="#C"/>euangelio capitulo III et IIII</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e189">penitentiam agite ap<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>propinquabit 
              enim regnum celorum</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e197">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Rd1e207">Idem 
              <lb ed="#C"/>capitulo V</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e199">beati qui lugent quoniam ipsi conso<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>labuntur </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e205">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Rd1e219">Lucas capitulo III</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e209">facite fruc<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tus 
              dignos penitentie</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e215">
              ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e217">Idem in actibus
              <lb ed="#C"/>apostolorum capitulo III peniteamini et conuerti<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>mini 
              ut deleantur peccata uestra</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e228">
              ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e232">paulus II
              <lb ed="#C"/>corinthinos VII Que secundum deum tristitia est peni<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tentiam 
              in salutem stabilem operatur
              <lb ed="#C"/>seculi autem tristitia mortem operatur</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e244">
              <lb ed="#C"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Rd1e260">Seneca tragediarum in agamenone capitulo 4o</ref> 
              <lb ed="#C"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e248">Quem penitet peccasse pene est innocens</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e256">
              <lb ed="#C"/>¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e258">Idem de naturalibus questionibus libro IIo fidelissimus
              <lb ed="#C"/>est qui ad honesta ex penitentia tran<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>sit</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e266">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Rd1e285">Cecilius firmianus de beata uita libro 3</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e270">
              <lb ed="#C"/>Multo firmior est fides quam reponit 
              <lb ed="#C"/>penitentia</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e284">
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Rd1e305">Ysidorus in sinonima
              <lb ed="#C"/>soliloquiorum libro I capitulo XII</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e288">Facile peniten<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tibus 
              diuina clementia subuenit per
              <lb ed="#C"/>penitentiam indulgentia datur per peni<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tentiam 
              delicta omnia absterguntur</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-d1e298">
              <lb ed="#C"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Rd1e322">Idem XVI capitulo et fidei</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de7543-Qd1e302">Inanis est peniten<lb ed="#C" break="no"/>tia 
              quam sequens culpa coinquinat</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
